source: TEXT_FESGSC2017_00383_ADVENTURE00383_000_000<tab>Don't think I haven't noticed you admiring my outfit! I bet you'd like to know where I got my hands on it, wouldn't you? Pay a visit to Ul'dah, ask around, and maybe you'll be lucky enough to find out!
target: TEXT_FESGSC2017_00383_ADVENTURE00383_000_000<tab>Vous aimez ma tenue<var 1D /var>? Je suis sûrrre que vous vous demandez où je l'ai dénichée<var 1D /var>! Allez à Ul'dah, et vous aurez toutes les réponses à vos questions<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_FESGSC2017_00383_ADVENTURE00383_000_100<tab>I see ye too find me attire to be quite fetchin'. Where did I get it, ye ask? Well, it'd hardly be fun if I just told ye now, would it? Go on o'er to Ul'dah and find out fer yerself!
target: TEXT_FESGSC2017_00383_ADVENTURE00383_000_100<tab>Elle est chouette cette tenue, vous ne trouvez pas<var 1D /var>? Vous vous demandez cer<var 16 /var>tai<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment où je l'ai eue<var 1D /var>! Eh bien si vous voulez le savoir, je vous recommande de faire un saut à Ul'dah<var 1D /var>!

source:
TEXT_FESGSC2017_00383_ADVENTURE00383_000_200I must say, that was quite something...
What's that? Why am I elated so? Why settle for hearing about my dreams when you could be living out your own? Head to Emerald Avenue and try asking around!
target: TEXT_FESGSC2017_00383_ADVENTURE00383_000_200<tab>J'ai jamais été aussi excitée de ma vie<var 1D /var>! Et si vous voulez savoir pourquoi, je vous conseille d'aller faire un tour à l'avenue de l'Émeraude<var 1D /var>!
